<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Reset Your {{app_name}} Password</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    <p>Hello {{data.full_name}},</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your {{app_name}} account password. Click the button below to create a new password:</p>
    
    <p><a href="{{data.reset_link}}" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 14px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">Reset Password</a></p>
    
    <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p>{{data.reset_link}}</p>
    
    <p>This link will expire in 1 hour for security reasons.</p>
    
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email and ensure your account is secure.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The {{app_name}} Team</p>
    
    <hr>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        For security concerns, please contact us immediately at {{support_email}}
    </p>
</body>
</html>
